name: Moguls of the Chef's Palette
description: Hailing from the Bogs of the <Anuran Countryside>, the Moguls of the Chef's Palette are known for cheffin up the good shit. That good good. Yeah. Now renowned portrayers - those who are able to summon their imaginings into reality via brushstroke, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
